WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.220
Good morning, everybody. I just wanted

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.080
to come on and tell you all a word

00:00:05.220 --> 00:00:09.000
that the Lord has for you today. I just

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:11.280
want to introduce my son, Braden.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:13.860
'Hey, what's up? I'm the editor

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:15.780
for 90% of his

00:00:13.860 --> 00:00:16.800
videos. I edit the shorts. You guys are being

00:00:15.780 --> 00:00:18.000
nice to me in the comments;

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:21.000
you're all asking, 'Who's the editor?'and

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.680
it was me.'The Lord's really gifted

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.180
him, and he's trying really hard.

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:26.759
'Yeah, I try to make them match. I try to do

00:00:24.180 --> 00:00:28.380
the math and stuff. It's a

00:00:26.760 --> 00:00:31.019
lot of work, but I hope you all enjoy it; it's fun.'He's

00:00:28.380 --> 00:00:32.519
15 years old. 'Yeah, I try to

00:00:31.019 --> 00:00:34.800
make the shorts,

00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:36.540
try to pick the topics and stuff. So if

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:38.099
you guys have any ideas for shorts, just

00:00:36.540 --> 00:00:39.839
let me know down in the comments so I

00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:41.399
can make some better shorts because

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:43.020
everybody seems to really like the end-time stuff—what's

00:00:41.399 --> 00:00:45.000
going to happen

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:47.399
and what we're fixing to head into.'This

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:49.200
is my son

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:50.820
right here;

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:52.860
I'm really proud of him. He works really

00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:55.739
hard, he's really smart, he does well

00:00:52.860 --> 00:00:58.320
at school, and he loves Jesus with

00:00:55.739 --> 00:01:00.899
all his heart. 'Yeah, I try really

00:00:58.320 --> 00:01:02.460
hard. I have a good upcoming short soon; I'm

00:01:00.899 --> 00:01:04.619
making it right now.'Oh, praise the Lord!

00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:06.479
I just wanted to

00:01:04.619 --> 00:01:08.159
bring him on here and show him

00:01:06.479 --> 00:01:11.340
off. I'm really proud of him and just

00:01:08.159 --> 00:01:14.460
tell people that he loves Jesus.

00:01:11.340 --> 00:01:16.439
I'm going to bring each one

00:01:14.460 --> 00:01:19.259
of my children on and introduce

00:01:16.439 --> 00:01:21.679
them to you all. This is the day I

00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:24.540
told him I wanted to introduce

00:01:24.540 --> 00:01:29.880
the man behind the camera. He's

00:01:26.820 --> 00:01:32.339
my prayer; he prays with me. He sits

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:33.780
with me every night and we intercede, and

00:01:32.340 --> 00:01:37.079
I'm teaching him how to intercede and

00:01:33.780 --> 00:01:39.240
dip in those rivers. He's

00:01:37.079 --> 00:01:40.979
learned a lot. We take communion. He was

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:44.158
there whenever we raised the dog from the

00:01:40.979 --> 00:01:45.720
dead. He was there whenever I

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:48.439
squashed the dog to death by accident.

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:50.759
Yeah, it was by accident.

00:01:48.439 --> 00:01:52.220
My wife's behind the camera right now;

00:01:52.220 --> 00:01:57.899
she's holding the camera. If

00:01:56.340 --> 00:01:59.880
you haven't seen that video, we'll link

00:01:57.899 --> 00:02:01.320
it in the description. God raised

00:01:59.880 --> 00:02:02.699
that dog from the dead; it was

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:05.758
special. Ever since he was a little

00:02:02.700 --> 00:02:06.960
baby boy in diapers, I've been

00:02:05.759 --> 00:02:08.280
teaching him. He's

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:09.959
been baptized in the Holy Ghost and

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:13.200
speaking in tongues since he was five

00:02:09.959 --> 00:02:15.300
years old. He sees in the spirit

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:17.459
too, and the Lord shows him things in

00:02:15.300 --> 00:02:19.140
dreams. It's the

00:02:17.459 --> 00:02:21.720
same with my daughter, and you'll meet

00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:23.819
her, probably in the next video—our youngest

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:26.040
daughter. Family is important to me, and

00:02:23.819 --> 00:02:27.899
I just wanted to

00:02:27.900 --> 00:02:32.760
show you all my son and

00:02:30.060 --> 00:02:36.500
introduce you. He's

00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:36.500
a real blessing. Okay,

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:45.300
about the spirit of forebodings

00:02:42.660 --> 00:02:47.459
and being in intercessory prayer.

00:02:45.300 --> 00:02:49.080
This is very important that you

00:02:47.459 --> 00:02:51.660
hear this because there are a lot of times

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:54.420
you can feel that heaviness—you feel

00:02:51.660 --> 00:02:55.980
that urge to intercede and

00:02:54.420 --> 00:02:58.379
you're in the moment and you're like, 'Man,

00:02:55.980 --> 00:03:00.000
I feel like there's a weight in the

00:02:58.379 --> 00:03:03.720
spirit realm on you.'What

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:07.680
happens is the demonic tries

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:09.599
to imitate the spiritual realm, and

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:11.819
the devil tries to push you into things—push,

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:13.679
push, push.

00:03:11.819 --> 00:03:15.540
This is one of the instances of

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:17.459
what I'm trying to tell you:

00:03:15.540 --> 00:03:18.599
you can walk around and always have a

00:03:17.459 --> 00:03:20.700
spirit of heaviness. It's like a

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:22.799
heaviness on you. You think, 'Well, it's the

00:03:20.700 --> 00:03:26.099
Lord and the burden to pray.'No,

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:28.680
it's not. There's a spirit of

00:03:26.099 --> 00:03:31.140
forebodings and it tries to come on and

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:33.959
push you into that place to

00:03:31.140 --> 00:03:36.720
make you not live in a state of joy.

00:03:33.959 --> 00:03:39.659
The fruit of the Spirit is love,

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:41.879
joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness,

00:03:39.659 --> 00:03:44.099
gentleness, and self-control. You need to

00:03:41.879 --> 00:03:46.319
understand that when you're not walking

00:03:44.099 --> 00:03:47.940
in that joy, when you're not walking in

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:50.458
the fruits of the Spirit, there's

00:03:47.940 --> 00:03:52.620
something wrong. To walk in the

00:03:50.459 --> 00:03:55.080
fruits of the Spirit, we have to have the

00:03:52.620 --> 00:03:58.080
preparation of the gospel of peace on

00:03:55.080 --> 00:04:00.060
our feet. If your shoes are not on your feet—the

00:03:58.080 --> 00:04:02.040
preparation of the gospel of peace—and

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:04.140
you're not walking in peace,

00:04:02.040 --> 00:04:06.900
you're barefoot and the rest of your

00:04:04.140 --> 00:04:09.298
armor is messed up because you have to

00:04:06.900 --> 00:04:11.819
have good shoes on to walk

00:04:09.299 --> 00:04:13.319
on the serpents and the scorpions with

00:04:11.819 --> 00:04:15.060
the shield of faith. You've got to have

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:17.639
all those things to quench all the

00:04:15.060 --> 00:04:19.440
fiery darts of the wicked. You need the sword of the Spirit, which is the word of God, to go and cut that devil up. You need to

00:04:17.639 --> 00:04:21.540
be able to have the

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:27.960
helmet of salvation

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:29.940
and

00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:32.039
the breastplate of righteousness.

00:04:29.940 --> 00:04:34.320
The spirit of

00:04:32.040 --> 00:04:37.259
forebodings will come and try to

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:40.080
torment you. You have got to take

00:04:37.259 --> 00:04:42.660
authority over that and make sure that

00:04:40.080 --> 00:04:44.758
whenever you're going into

00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:47.460
intercession, you're not being

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:49.680
tormented by a spirit of forebodings—a

00:04:47.460 --> 00:04:51.900
fearful apprehension, a feeling that

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:54.180
something bad is about to happen.

00:04:51.900 --> 00:04:56.638
You've got to make sure that spirit

00:04:54.180 --> 00:04:58.979
is not pushing you: 'Something bad's about

00:04:56.639 --> 00:05:00.720
to happen, we got to intercede.'We got to

00:04:58.979 --> 00:05:02.520
walk that way. That's the way it was

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:04.440
for me forever. I had that for years,

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:07.020
always walking around thinking something

00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:09.479
bad was about to happen. 'Oh no, I feel

00:05:07.020 --> 00:05:11.820
heaviness, it must be...'And when

00:05:09.479 --> 00:05:14.219
the Lord showed me this, He said,

00:05:11.820 --> 00:05:15.960
'Brandon, this is a spirit of foreboding

00:05:14.220 --> 00:05:17.699
that's bothering you all the

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:19.620
time. This isn't a spirit of intercession;

00:05:17.699 --> 00:05:21.960
you need to be able to learn

00:05:19.620 --> 00:05:24.360
the discernment of how to

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:26.039
divide it.'So I started taking

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:28.800
authority, and if I start to feel

00:05:26.039 --> 00:05:30.599
that or anything like that, I go, 'Uh-uh. Is

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:33.000
this a spirit of forebodings, or is this

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:35.100
the Holy Ghost leading me to start

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:37.139
interceding for something?'When you

00:05:35.100 --> 00:05:39.840
start binding that spirit back and say,

00:05:37.139 --> 00:05:41.880
'No, I will not yield to a spirit of

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:43.739
forebodings, but I will yield to the Holy

00:05:41.880 --> 00:05:45.960
Ghost and I will pray in the Holy Ghost

00:05:43.740 --> 00:05:47.520
right now,'I bind any spirit; you're

00:05:45.960 --> 00:05:49.919
not going to torment me because I'm not

00:05:47.520 --> 00:05:53.280
going to walk in torment. Fear hath

00:05:49.919 --> 00:05:55.799
torment, but perfect love casteth out all

00:05:53.280 --> 00:05:57.479
fear. You can't allow that to happen

00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:58.860
because I'm telling you, you'll start

00:05:57.479 --> 00:06:00.479
crawling underneath that rock every day,

00:05:58.860 --> 00:06:02.100
and it'll keep leading you

00:06:00.479 --> 00:06:03.780
that way, and you'll live in

00:06:02.100 --> 00:06:07.380
a heaviness and go around like Eeyore—you

00:06:03.780 --> 00:06:09.960
know, 'woe is me, everything's

00:06:07.380 --> 00:06:11.460
falling apart.'You can't do that. You've

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:14.239
got to be the Tigger and go,

00:06:11.460 --> 00:06:16.620
'Hey, ha ha, I got joy!'I

00:06:14.240 --> 00:06:18.360
hate to use that as an illustration,

00:06:16.620 --> 00:06:19.919
y'all, but

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:22.440
when you have kids, you see Winnie the

00:06:19.919 --> 00:06:25.620
Pooh. Walk in the spirit of joy, walk

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:27.060
in peace, walk in the

00:06:25.620 --> 00:06:29.940
fruits of the Spirit. Another thing I

00:06:27.060 --> 00:06:32.759
need to tell you: the Holy Spirit is a

00:06:29.940 --> 00:06:35.819
person. He's a gentleman, and

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:39.600
when you invite Him into your life, He

00:06:35.819 --> 00:06:41.400
will... last night

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:43.740
I was worshiping and He

00:06:41.400 --> 00:06:45.719
said, 'You've dumped out enough

00:06:43.740 --> 00:06:47.880
through these videos. You need to fill

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:49.740
yourself back up. I need to spend some

00:06:47.880 --> 00:06:52.259
time with you. I need you to separate

00:06:49.740 --> 00:06:53.819
yourself for a while now.'Before

00:06:52.259 --> 00:06:55.800
all the videos, it

00:06:53.819 --> 00:06:57.479
has been a big adjustment

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:58.440
for me because the time

00:06:57.479 --> 00:07:00.300
that I'm doing these videos or

00:06:58.440 --> 00:07:02.940
answering your comments, I used to spend

00:07:00.300 --> 00:07:04.800
in prayer and worship and

00:07:02.940 --> 00:07:06.360
seeking Him. And He said, 'I need you to just

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:08.280
take your time and separate right now.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:10.080
Don't make a video; don't think

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:11.818
about a video. I need you to dip in the

00:07:10.080 --> 00:07:14.039
river right now. I need you to do this

00:07:11.819 --> 00:07:17.340
for Me.'And I stopped and I said, 'Well,

00:07:14.039 --> 00:07:18.599
okay, Lord.'And the presence of God

00:07:17.340 --> 00:07:19.560
took a little bit, and I

00:07:18.600 --> 00:07:20.940
started getting in there. I started

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:22.919
singing the song. Like I'm telling y'all,

00:07:20.940 --> 00:07:24.840
I worship Him, and in His presence,

00:07:22.919 --> 00:07:25.919
there's fullness of joy.

00:07:24.840 --> 00:07:27.119
I said,

00:07:25.919 --> 00:07:30.000
'Worship Him,'and I start singing songs

00:07:27.120 --> 00:07:31.919
and I get into His presence. I will enter His gates with

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:33.780
thanksgiving in

00:07:31.919 --> 00:07:35.698
my heart;

00:07:33.780 --> 00:07:37.099
I enter into those

00:07:35.699 --> 00:07:39.780
courts,

00:07:37.099 --> 00:07:42.240
and I will enter in

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:49.919
His courts with praise. I will say this

00:07:45.539 --> 00:07:52.740
is the day that the Lord has made. I will

00:07:49.919 --> 00:07:55.979
rejoice and be glad...

00:07:52.740 --> 00:08:00.539
He has made me glad, He has made me glad,

00:07:55.979 --> 00:08:03.840
I will rejoice for He has made me glad.

00:08:00.539 --> 00:08:07.620
You have to get there. You have to

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:11.219
train yourself to step into that glory

00:08:07.620 --> 00:08:13.440
river, and the more you do it, the easier

00:08:11.220 --> 00:08:15.840
and faster you get there. It's like

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:17.699
a

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:19.739
muscle. You keep lifting those spiritual

00:08:17.699 --> 00:08:21.240
weights, you keep working out, and you'll

00:08:19.740 --> 00:08:23.479
start jumping in those rivers really

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:23.479
quick.

00:08:23.580 --> 00:08:29.099
Honestly, when people say, 'Oh, my prayer

00:08:25.919 --> 00:08:30.000
life is so

00:08:29.099 --> 00:08:32.880
dry,'you've

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:34.860
got to push

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:37.799
through those dry times. You don't give

00:08:34.860 --> 00:08:39.000
up. You keep pushing through

00:08:37.799 --> 00:08:40.799
that wall

00:08:40.799 --> 00:08:46.680
by prayer, thanksgiving, and worship.

00:08:46.680 --> 00:08:49.859
When you get through that wall, you'll

00:08:48.180 --> 00:08:51.719
get into the river,

00:08:49.860 --> 00:08:54.060
you'll get in this gusher,

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:55.860
and

00:08:54.060 --> 00:08:58.018
you'll start getting into that flow so

00:08:55.860 --> 00:09:00.300
strong. And that's whenever He'll

00:08:58.019 --> 00:09:02.459
start taking you places. I'll

00:09:00.300 --> 00:09:04.979
start interceding about things,

00:09:02.459 --> 00:09:07.920
and I'll hear... what's really cool, and

00:09:04.980 --> 00:09:09.839
I hope this is kind of

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:11.819
deep,

00:09:09.839 --> 00:09:14.339
but you all need a little bit of

00:09:11.820 --> 00:09:16.560
deep today. I

00:09:14.339 --> 00:09:20.040
can hear the prayers of the

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:22.560
intercessors outside. A lot

00:09:20.040 --> 00:09:25.019
of times, I'll go into the spirit and I

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:27.180
can hear. I listen for this one

00:09:25.019 --> 00:09:28.980
elderly woman—I know she's elderly; I

00:09:28.980 --> 00:09:33.839
assume she's probably in her 80s because

00:09:31.680 --> 00:09:36.540
she knows how to flow

00:09:33.839 --> 00:09:39.300
in the rivers big time—and it's

00:09:36.540 --> 00:09:40.920
almost like a heartbeat. You can start

00:09:39.300 --> 00:09:42.719
going in the spirit realm like a

00:09:40.920 --> 00:09:46.019
heartbeat with people in other parts

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:48.660
of the world, and you start to sway in,

00:09:46.019 --> 00:09:50.700
and like a fish,

00:09:48.660 --> 00:09:52.740
you're swimming in the stream with them.

00:09:50.700 --> 00:09:54.800
You can start swimming in the stream in

00:09:52.740 --> 00:09:57.480
the spirit with them. I

00:09:54.800 --> 00:10:01.140
notice

00:09:57.480 --> 00:10:03.480
these intercessors,

00:10:01.140 --> 00:10:06.000
and the Lord will call me beside them

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:07.500
even in my own home. I've never met these

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:09.600
people, but when I get to heaven, I know I

00:10:07.500 --> 00:10:11.100
will. I can go beside them because they

00:10:09.600 --> 00:10:12.720
always pray at a certain time and I

00:10:11.100 --> 00:10:15.660
always pray at certain times,

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:18.060
and they'll go. But inside me, we'll

00:10:15.660 --> 00:10:19.680
pray and we'll flow in the spirit realm

00:10:18.060 --> 00:10:22.439
with them. I can

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:25.079
feel it, and it's like a

00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:26.880
symphony; it's beautiful music. It's a

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:29.040
symphony, but we're praying and we're

00:10:26.880 --> 00:10:30.839
bringing down the strongholds,

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:34.140
setting people

00:10:30.839 --> 00:10:36.720
free and the captives free.

00:10:34.140 --> 00:10:39.360
The spirit realm is more real

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:42.959
than the natural. I hope you all realize

00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:46.140
the spirit realm is so real.

00:10:42.959 --> 00:10:48.300
It's so amazing what goes on when you

00:10:46.140 --> 00:10:50.399
start tapping into the rivers and you

00:10:48.300 --> 00:10:53.459
start going in with the Holy Ghost and

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:55.500
flowing with Him in intercessory prayer.

00:10:53.459 --> 00:10:57.479
You'll start to notice people; you'll

00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:59.160
start to notice their heartbeat. You can

00:10:57.480 --> 00:11:00.540
feel them in the spirit realm when

00:10:59.160 --> 00:11:01.800
you're praying. I'm not talking about

00:11:00.540 --> 00:11:04.319
being weird, because some of you

00:11:01.800 --> 00:11:05.640
get really weird, you know, talking

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:07.920
to angels and doing all that stuff.

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:12.060
I'm not talking about that. You pray,

00:11:07.920 --> 00:11:14.040
and you can get into some

00:11:12.060 --> 00:11:15.899
really cool stuff in the

00:11:14.040 --> 00:11:19.079
spirit realm when you're praying and you

00:11:15.899 --> 00:11:20.880
grow spiritually. This is

00:11:19.079 --> 00:11:22.500
big boy stuff, big girl stuff.

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:24.839
This isn't little baby stuff I'm

00:11:22.500 --> 00:11:27.899
talking about; this is deep.

00:11:24.839 --> 00:11:29.640
This is going to the deep rivers.

00:11:27.899 --> 00:11:31.200
I'm trying to tell you all, there's

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:33.060
a spirit on this you don't

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:36.240
have a clue about. A lot of you

