are clueless about what goes on,

00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:42.000
even in the cults and the things

00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:44.579
they do.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:48.000
It's time for the body of Christ to grow

00:11:44.579 --> 00:11:50.519
up and start eating the meat. It's time

