like I said, I

00:12:16.620 --> 00:12:20.040
could hear the people in Africa praying.

00:12:18.540 --> 00:12:21.839
I can hear the people in Asia praying.

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:26.480
You can go in and out of those veins

00:12:21.839 --> 00:12:26.480
