00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:31.500
The body of Christ is so

00:12:29.279 --> 00:12:34.980
cool. The spirit realm is so cool, y'all.

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:37.560
Number two: I was down and

00:12:34.980 --> 00:12:39.300
really having a hard time. I was

00:12:37.560 --> 00:12:41.219
at my mom and dad's church visiting,

00:12:39.300 --> 00:12:44.180
and

00:12:44.339 --> 00:12:48.660
I was worshiping. I was dealing with

00:12:46.740 --> 00:12:50.160
some heaviness—those

00:12:48.660 --> 00:12:51.839
forebodings I was telling you all

00:12:50.160 --> 00:12:54.480
about just a little bit ago.

00:12:51.839 --> 00:12:56.579
I was worshiping in their church, and

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:59.639
all of a sudden there was a portal that

00:12:56.579 --> 00:13:02.339
opened up—a massive gateway. A portal

00:12:59.639 --> 00:13:05.839
opened up in

00:13:02.339 --> 00:13:09.839
the front of the church. I could see

00:13:05.839 --> 00:13:12.240
the ground;

00:13:09.839 --> 00:13:13.860
it was split where the portal

00:13:12.240 --> 00:13:17.100
was. There was a huge circular

00:13:13.860 --> 00:13:19.019
portal; it was purple and pink and

00:13:17.100 --> 00:13:22.019
all kinds of beautiful

00:13:19.019 --> 00:13:23.880
colors. It looked like cotton

00:13:22.019 --> 00:13:26.700
candy,

00:13:23.880 --> 00:13:29.820
like a Holy Ghost fog. It

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:32.820
was beautiful. Jesus walks in with

00:13:29.820 --> 00:13:35.040
these angels—massive warring

00:13:32.820 --> 00:13:36.720
angels. This is the

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:39.959
first time I've ever seen Jesus with

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:43.019
angels like this. He walks in and

00:13:39.959 --> 00:13:45.599
stands before me. Behind

00:13:43.019 --> 00:13:49.019
where the portal was, it lifted up and I could see

00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:51.120
all these feet.

00:13:49.019 --> 00:13:53.100
They were barefoot;

00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:54.839
none of them had shoes on. I could

00:13:53.100 --> 00:13:56.880
see gowns and robes, again like

00:13:54.839 --> 00:14:00.180
what I told you I saw in

00:13:56.880 --> 00:14:02.519
heaven.

00:14:00.180 --> 00:14:04.560
I asked Jesus, 'What

00:14:02.519 --> 00:14:07.680
are all the feet?'and He said, 'That is

00:14:04.560 --> 00:14:09.839
part of the great cloud of witnesses, and

00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:12.180
they've come to watch the service and what's

00:14:09.839 --> 00:14:14.279
going on here right now.'I

00:14:12.180 --> 00:14:16.260
could hear them all talking.

00:14:14.279 --> 00:14:18.180
You know how when you get in a

00:14:16.260 --> 00:14:19.800
crowd you can't really understand what

00:14:18.180 --> 00:14:22.079
they're saying because when you hear a

00:14:19.800 --> 00:14:24.180
lot of voices together they're saying something—I

00:14:22.079 --> 00:14:26.819
could hear all the

00:14:24.180 --> 00:14:28.680
voices talking, but I couldn't make

00:14:26.820 --> 00:14:30.000
out what they were

00:14:28.680 --> 00:14:31.859
saying.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:34.380
There was

00:14:31.860 --> 00:14:36.660
activity going on in heaven, but they

00:14:34.380 --> 00:14:38.579
were watching.

00:14:36.660 --> 00:14:40.560
I could see their

00:14:38.579 --> 00:14:42.719
gowns and everything behind

00:14:40.560 --> 00:14:45.540
when Jesus opened up the portal. The

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:47.339
portal lifted up and I could see in there—some

00:14:45.540 --> 00:14:49.319
trees and

00:14:47.339 --> 00:14:51.300
some stuff going on—but all I

00:14:49.320 --> 00:14:53.459
could see was from their feet to the

00:14:51.300 --> 00:14:55.380
middle of their waist.

00:14:53.459 --> 00:14:57.899
They were all lined up and

00:14:55.380 --> 00:14:59.699
looking from

00:14:57.899 --> 00:15:02.339
heaven into Earth at what was going on

00:14:59.699 --> 00:15:05.579
in the service.

00:15:05.579 --> 00:15:11.339
The

00:15:08.940 --> 00:15:14.160
King of Kings visited, and it was

00:15:11.339 --> 00:15:17.100
amazing; the

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:19.860
glory was so thick. Jesus came up

00:15:17.100 --> 00:15:21.899
to me and

00:15:19.860 --> 00:15:23.820
stood right in

00:15:21.899 --> 00:15:25.920
front of me. It was in the spirit; it

00:15:23.820 --> 00:15:27.600
wasn't a full manifestation like flesh

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:30.060
to flesh, like I had in my kitchen

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:31.860
whenever He visited me that time. That

00:15:30.060 --> 00:15:33.959
was too intense; I

00:15:31.860 --> 00:15:35.399
collapsed. But I stood like this in the

00:15:33.959 --> 00:15:38.339
spirit realm and could see over in the

00:15:35.399 --> 00:15:42.000
spirit, and Jesus told me,

00:15:38.339 --> 00:15:43.380
'My yoke is easy and my burden is

00:15:42.000 --> 00:15:45.600
light, Brandon.

00:15:43.380 --> 00:15:48.180
You're thinking way too much.

00:15:45.600 --> 00:15:50.339
You're meditating

00:15:48.180 --> 00:15:52.920
on the wrong thoughts way too much.'He

00:15:50.339 --> 00:15:55.740
said, 'I want you

00:15:52.920 --> 00:15:57.599
to

00:15:55.740 --> 00:16:01.320
take the care out of your prayer.

00:15:57.600 --> 00:16:03.480
Be careful for nothing, son; you're

00:16:01.320 --> 00:16:06.000
full of care.'He

00:16:03.480 --> 00:16:09.660
said, 'Do you see

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:10.800
this box?'I was inside a big wooden

00:16:09.660 --> 00:16:13.920
box

00:16:10.800 --> 00:16:16.439
and I was trying so hard to get out,

00:16:13.920 --> 00:16:18.660
but I believed I was

00:16:16.440 --> 00:16:20.940
in this box and that it had a lid on it

00:16:18.660 --> 00:16:22.740
and I was trapped.

00:16:24.959 --> 00:16:30.300
I was so bound by fear and

00:16:27.839 --> 00:16:31.740
torment all the time because of things I

00:16:30.300 --> 00:16:33.599
felt

00:16:31.740 --> 00:16:35.540
were going on in the world, in my family,

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:37.560
and my house—a lot of

00:16:35.540 --> 00:16:38.819
occultist stuff. It was rough

00:16:37.560 --> 00:16:41.099
at that time.

00:16:41.100 --> 00:16:46.199
Jesus said, 'Brandon, there's

00:16:43.380 --> 00:16:47.639
no lid on the box. You're set free. All

00:16:46.199 --> 00:16:50.160
you've got to do is get out of the box.

00:16:47.639 --> 00:16:52.380
Your thoughts are

00:16:50.160 --> 00:16:53.699
why you're in the box. You're

00:16:52.380 --> 00:16:55.560
meditating on the

00:16:53.699 --> 00:16:57.660
wrong things. You need to start

00:16:55.560 --> 00:17:00.119
meditating on the right thing. Get in my

00:16:57.660 --> 00:17:01.800
word and meditate on my word.

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:03.779
You're meditating too much on the news and

00:17:01.800 --> 00:17:06.119
these

00:17:03.779 --> 00:17:08.819
wrong things. My yoke is easy

00:17:06.119 --> 00:17:10.859
and my burden is light.'He told me,

00:17:10.859 --> 00:17:14.458
'You've got to stop thinking so much. You

00:17:12.900 --> 00:17:16.620
think way too much.'And He started

00:17:14.459 --> 00:17:18.179
laughing. Jesus started laughing at the circumstances.

00:17:16.619 --> 00:17:20.159
He said, 'Brandon, you've got to start

00:17:18.179 --> 00:17:22.020
laughing. You've got to start enjoying life.'He

00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:24.179
started laughing, and His

00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:25.918
laugh was so beautiful. It was so

00:17:24.179 --> 00:17:27.839
deep; He chuckled and laughed.

00:17:25.919 --> 00:17:30.120
He had beautiful, white, perfect straight

00:17:27.839 --> 00:17:31.799
teeth.

00:17:30.120 --> 00:17:34.080
He just laughed and

00:17:31.799 --> 00:17:37.139
was rejoicing, like, 'You've got

00:17:34.080 --> 00:17:38.520
to laugh!'I

00:17:37.140 --> 00:17:40.679
was fixed on His face.

00:17:38.520 --> 00:17:42.600
I'd

00:17:40.679 --> 00:17:45.900
never seen Jesus laugh like

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:47.219
this. Everything has

00:17:45.900 --> 00:17:48.960
always been real serious when I've had

00:17:47.220 --> 00:17:50.160
these visitations, but

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:51.480
this time He was

00:17:50.160 --> 00:17:53.280
laughing and telling me

00:17:51.480 --> 00:17:57.000
it's time to be full of joy.

00:17:53.280 --> 00:18:00.059
He said I had black smudges

00:17:57.000 --> 00:18:02.120
on my clothes and on me from all of

00:18:00.059 --> 00:18:04.799
the

00:18:02.120 --> 00:18:06.899
demonic pressure that I was allowing in

00:18:04.799 --> 00:18:08.700
my life by my thought life.

00:18:08.700 --> 00:18:12.660
I'm not going to tell you anything

00:18:09.900 --> 00:18:14.100
else He said because it's private, but He

00:18:12.660 --> 00:18:16.559
was just ministering to me.

00:18:14.100 --> 00:18:18.178
He lifted me up

00:18:16.559 --> 00:18:20.220
and showed me how to get out of that

00:18:18.179 --> 00:18:22.919
box and get in the word.

00:18:22.919 --> 00:18:28.140
The presence of God was

00:18:25.919 --> 00:18:30.120
so thick in that service that night.

00:18:30.120 --> 00:18:35.340
The power of God

00:18:33.059 --> 00:18:37.678
set me free, and I've never been the same

00:18:35.340 --> 00:18:40.080
since.

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:44.639
These visitations

00:18:46.320 --> 00:18:50.700
have

00:18:53.700 --> 00:18:58.679
changed my life,

00:18:57.120 --> 00:19:01.199
and I've come to tell you these things

00:18:58.679 --> 00:19:03.720
because Jesus wants to change your life.

00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:05.880
He wants to love on you and tell you

00:19:03.720 --> 00:19:08.280
how much He loves you.

00:19:05.880 --> 00:19:10.440
I just wanted to

00:19:08.280 --> 00:19:13.740
encourage you all today that His yoke is easy and His burden is

00:19:10.440 --> 00:19:16.260
light.

00:19:13.740 --> 00:19:18.840
Don't walk in a spirit of heaviness; walk

00:19:16.260 --> 00:19:21.600
in a garment of praise. Be in that place

00:19:18.840 --> 00:19:23.520
of joy in your life because Jesus loves

00:19:21.600 --> 00:19:25.320
you so much.

00:19:23.520 --> 00:19:27.840
There's a great

00:19:25.320 --> 00:19:29.520
cloud of witnesses watching us,

00:19:27.840 --> 00:19:31.080
smiling and

00:19:29.520 --> 00:19:33.360
cheering us on.

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:46.080
We have such a short amount of

00:19:42.539 --> 00:19:48.840
time before we get to go home.

00:19:46.080 --> 00:19:50.639
Jesus is coming, and I hope this

00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:53.280
blessed you today.

00:19:50.640 --> 00:19:55.500
Father, I

00:19:53.280 --> 00:19:59.220
thank You that You

00:19:55.500 --> 00:20:02.640
are bringing a spirit of peace and

00:19:59.220 --> 00:20:05.460
joy over their lives

00:20:02.640 --> 00:20:08.160
today. I thank You that

00:20:05.460 --> 00:20:10.679
there's a garment of praise. We give

00:20:08.160 --> 00:20:12.780
You that praise because You're worthy. We

00:20:10.679 --> 00:20:15.360
give You the honor and glory because You

00:20:12.780 --> 00:20:17.039
deserve every bit of it, Lord. You've cleansed

00:20:15.360 --> 00:20:19.199
us from all

00:20:17.039 --> 00:20:21.720
unrighteousness. You've taken away all the

00:20:19.200 --> 00:20:24.299
sin from our lives. You took the sickness

00:20:21.720 --> 00:20:27.000
and disease on your body. You took

00:20:24.299 --> 00:20:28.860
poverty for us, Father. I thank you. Mental torment—you

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:31.020
took it. When they put

00:20:28.860 --> 00:20:33.539
that crown of thorns on your head, you

00:20:31.020 --> 00:20:36.418
took that on you, Father. You said that

00:20:33.539 --> 00:20:38.220
you took all those things; you became

00:20:36.419 --> 00:20:41.280
those things so that we don't have to go

00:20:38.220 --> 00:20:44.220
through them. What Jesus bore in his

00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:46.980
body, I need not bear in mine. I thank

00:20:44.220 --> 00:20:49.559
you, Father, that you've set me free by

00:20:46.980 --> 00:20:52.020
the blood of the lamb and by the

00:20:49.559 --> 00:20:54.899
word of my testimony. My testimony is

00:20:52.020 --> 00:20:57.360
great: Jesus Christ is my Lord and Savior.

00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:59.100
I thank you all for joining

00:20:57.360 --> 00:21:01.620
me today.

00:20:59.100 --> 00:21:03.178
I thank you all for being a part of

00:21:01.620 --> 00:21:06.479
this little community, my family

00:21:03.179 --> 00:21:08.760
here. I thank you. Please like my

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:11.160
videos and share them; it really helps me

00:21:08.760 --> 00:21:13.500
with the algorithm. Put a smile on your

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:16.200
